post_title: Joe Doyle Blank Back SGC A (1-of-1)
post_content:
This is a very special card.  It's the only known Joe Doyle Blank Back. If you want a rare back for Doyle, this is your one and only option.  Other than this card, you'd have to settle for a Tolstoi or EPDG, which are his other toughest backs.


$4500 ppff SOLD
